metadata.name: Rain or Shine
metadata.description:
A couple in ponchos huddles to read a festival program in a rainstorm during the Fuji Rock Festival in Niigata, Japan, on July 24, 2009. 

Photograph created by Rebecca Smeyne for the Village Voice, while on assignment at Fuji Rock. Image is part of a long-term body of professional work documenting cultural scenes.
